reviewText: Good story. Loved Justin Timberlake in this movie!
Decent dystopian movie when we all have a life battery that needs to be recharged and the rich have all the charge they want. Seems unfair like God made the world, eh?
Great Movie, love Justin Timberlake and Amanda Seyfried in this futuristic syfi movie about Time is Money.
I like it, cool little movie. Its not great or very memorable. The story is kinda interesting, but also very silly (which is bad, because they are trying to be serious about it).
Excellent movie, defiantly ranks in my top ten.
My love of Cillian Murphy has brought me to some dark places, and this is one of the darkest.
Movie was your fanciful endeavor of immortality, sad it falls short at the end.
